channel.title: Wreck it Ralph - Disneymovie based off videogames
channel.description:
![](upload://fovfrAuO9VC3wo8Z2XEuxlAjPd8.png)
[url='https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GHDQHVkYq4g&feature=player_embedded']Official first trailer[/url]
Looking forward to it.
The film tells the story of Wreck-It Ralph (Reilly), an arcade video game "bad guy", who is determined to prove he can be a good guy. The movie comes out on 2nd November in the USA. Many videogame characters are going to have cameos in it, you can already see Bowser and a ghost from Pac-Man in the trailer.
[i]The cast, according to wikipedia:
John C. Reilly as Wreck-It Ralph Jack McBrayer as Fix-It Felix Jr. Jane Lynch as Sergeant Calhoun Sarah Silverman as Vanellope von Schweetz Jamie Elman as Turtle Stefanie Scott as TBA TBA as Doctor Eggman from Sonic the Hedgehog TBA as Tigor TBA as Zangief from Street Fighter II TBA as Zombie
Concept art for the film has suggested that Wreck-It Ralph will feature cameo appearances from a number of video game characters. The characters exhibited thus far include:
Bowser from Super Mario Bros. Clyde from Pac-Man Q*Bert and Coily the Snake from Q*bert Doctor Wily from Mega Man Kano from Mortal Kombat Chun Li and M. Bison from Street Fighter II[/i]
Chun Li is also in the background on the image above.
